entries.journal_entry_description: Captain Typho has some unclassified Marine missions that need to be completed.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Eliminate some of the more dangerous leaders of the Mauler organization. Start with their chief Tactician, Zolo Sartain. First, make your way back to the Mauler Stronghold.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: We're going to start with Zolo Sartain, the chief tactician for the Maulers.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Find and eliminate Zolo Sartain, the chief tactician for the Maulers.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Excellent work. Now, I want you to deal with Yarick Tempol, the head of Mauler Security.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find and eliminate Yarick Tempol, the head of Mauler security.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: The assassin, Xylan Kee'choap is your next target. Keep up the good work.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Find and eliminate the assassin, Xylan Kee'choap, who works exclusively for the Maulers.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: The next one is the last one and the toughest one. Walus Mutin is a mystic. Be wary. He may be more dangerous than you expect.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Find and eliminate Walus Mutin, the Zabrak mystic, who they say wields a lightsaber similar to Darth Maul's.
entries.task09_comm_message_text: Impressive work. Return to me now that you've completed your assignment. It's great to finally find someone who can accomplish these kinds of tasks.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Return to Typho so he can finish up his paperwork for this assignment.
